$ svnlook help
general usage: svnlook SUBCOMMAND REPOS_PATH [ARGS &amp; OPTIONS ...]
Note: any subcommand which takes the &#39;--revision&#39; and &#39;--transaction&#39;
      options will, if invoked without one of those options, act on
